Corporate Event Venue Orlando
When it comes to delivering a special or corporate event to remember, no place does it better than Mango’s.
With high-tech, widescreen plasmas throughout, a multi-million dollar state-of-the-art sound and video system makes this Caribbean paradise not only one of the most upscale destinations on I-Drive, but also the premier private party and event space in the city.
Mango’s talented culinary team offers an extensive
menu
of gourmet Floribbean fare, a unique blend of Caribbean and Latin-inspired dishes, as well as custom menus for private parties, and the world’s longest list of lemonade and classic mojitos, caipirinhas, daiquiris and margaritas.
Our extensive list of past clients include Fortune 500 companies in the financial, medical and hospitality industries from 20 guests to 3,000.
